    "en": {
      "title": "Two killed in motorcycle van accident",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Badalgama Police say that two people have died and one person has been injured in an accident that happened near the Tammita Library on Badalgama road in Maradagahamula.",
        "P., a resident of Kehelalle, died in the accident that occurred when a motorcycle collided with a van. that. Asitha Rangana (37) is a businessman named Chinthaka Pushpakumara, 38, father of one who is an electrician and father of two who lives in Tammi.",
        "At the time of the accident, three people were traveling on the motorcycle, two of them died and the other injured person was admitted to the Negombo District Hospital."
      ],
